// Core library: the Map collection.
//
// `Map<K, V>` is an engine-provided persistent map. Its whole surface —
// `empty`, `get`, `insert`, `remove`, `contains`, `length`, `keys`,
// `values` — is a set of intrinsics that compile to dedicated opcodes;
// they attach to this module at registration (`intrinsics_for_module`),
// so it carries no source declarations of its own.
